headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Discounts
content:
Make sure you’ve got enough room for your car collection: Garages of all sizes are 40% off. Plus, there are discounts offered on a range of vehicles, land, air, and sea alike:

- P-45 Nokota – 30% off
- RM-10 Bombushka – 30% off
- Übermacht Revolter – 30% off
- Western Cargobob – 40% off

And More! Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
